{
  "stem": "293.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he want to send them back to some other camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "She told him, when you will not let these people out till Mr.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Schindler will come over.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We need the people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "You will go to Eastern Front.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "You know that Mr.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Schindler has a connection in Berlin.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So don't interfere.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "He let her wait till Schindler come in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And Schindler come in and called the world as Mr.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Mandela and me-- there were two-- to come over because you can open the door.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "You have to move the snow.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And you have to cut the hinges.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "We cut the hinges and we took the door.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "From this 136, 16 was dead.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And the rest, another five hours, four hours, two hours, they all will be dead.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "They were frozen.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "They were-- some of those lost ears, part ears, toes, part of nose.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Someway, somehow, Mrs.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Schindler and Oskar Schindler put upon themselves to play angels.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And they doed everything possible to save those people's lives.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "They never work.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "He has to pay 600 marks for each of us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "So even for those people who didn't work, he'd pay for them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "She found medication, what was necessary, on the black market in-- in Sudetenland.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And they saved this life of about 115, 120 people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "No, 16 was dead so-- and then couple more die later on, but over 100 Golleschau people survived.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And they survived the war, and they brought to life.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And the most dramatic item was this-- that he got the order to burn the body in the oven, over there in the factory [NON-ENGLISH], the big oven.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And Schindler refused.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "He said, in my factory, you don't burn body.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "We bury them.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
